title: #92Noon! Boudreau/McGinest/Charch/Gleeman/Brick
description: Bruce Boudreau and Willie McGinest both join in the first hour on the Wild's preseason opener and NFL nuggets, respectively. Then a lonnnnng segment of Vikings calls & opinions, followed by Charch's Pickup Joint. Gleeman in studio most of the final hour with JT the Brick closing the show!
